{"tid":1069633,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(無圖) 尋蟲記","createTime":"2019-03-20T05:59:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T10:26:59.000Z","uid":76970,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"94bfc8d5f250a2ae68639bbec4a53e802a9efc27","tid":1069633,"uid":76970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T05:59:06.000Z","msg":"同事張枱無啦啦彈左隻蟲仔出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚇到全公司班女同事雞飛狗走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果出動哂全公司男同事係度捉蟲蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n追溯到源頭竟然係公司電話度走黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FivcEhz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFivcEhz.jpg&h=c55a6e04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲拆開部電話，成堆蟲蟲屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9uU5eQT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9uU5eQT.jpg&h=898b6dc4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n▲出現了，好大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jzp8W4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjzp8W4f.jpg&h=038d75b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲仲有蟲卵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HMD5ZhA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHMD5ZhA.jpg&h=1b1d3055&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zr9XQpd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzr9XQpd.jpg&h=0e67a4df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲唧爆粒蟲卵竟然係綠色架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請問各位全能既連登仔呢隻係乜野黎，點樣根治<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好答我用火攻/津路水炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955cf1a320e3db6040bc98f73800b25b452528dc","tid":1069633,"uid":131836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T06:01:00.000Z","msg":"放兩日假休息"},{"pid":"be0458a162c3b41b6cebe919197a9bf084db0656","tid":1069633,"uid":76970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"955cf1a320e3db6040bc98f73800b25b452528dc","tid":1069633,"uid":131836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T06:01:00.000Z","msg":"放兩日假休息"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T06:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過兩日咪又返黎"},{"pid":"be9c41340c06e8fc5c68facbbf1fa7140df436f5","tid":1069633,"uid":6703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T06:10:18.000Z","msg":"唔係小強黎咩"},{"pid":"def114d9d537ebd91bf25404a32badad05ce2fae","tid":1069633,"uid":31071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T06:12:09.000Z","msg":"下世唔好唧爆粒野佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9214cd4becfaab4845e885ef44c619ee72c66c","tid":1069633,"uid":76970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be9c41340c0